  "texts": [
    "While P-tuning is effective in larger models, it lags behind other methods in smaller models, particularly for RETRO.",
    "Applying PEFT to Instructiontuned RETRO yields limited improvement compared to base RETRO, suggesting a saturation point in leveraging pre-training and fine-tuning benefits.",
    "Our comprehensive analysis offers valuable insights for optimizing large language models with PEFT and RAG to the community.",
    "Due to the breadth of experiments covered in this work we had to prioritze certain experiments over others.",
    "This resulted in us using only the small and medium sized GPT and RETRO models for additional finetuning and Instruction tuning experiments."
  ],
